ɕint͡ɕiŋpaokʰuaiɕyn（t͡ɕiʈ͡ʂeɕinnuo）t͡ɕinɻi，isoupanamat͡ɕijouʈ͡ʂʰuanjuʈ͡ʂoŋkuoɕiaŋkaŋt͡ɕisanxuoʈ͡ʂʰuanɕiaŋʈ͡ʂuaŋ，ʈ͡ʂʰuanʂaŋjunt͡saitiniŋɕijouɕielou。t͡ɕinɻi，kuot͡ɕiaxaijaŋt͡ɕyʈ͡ʂuant͡ɕiafenɕiʈ͡ʂʰeŋ，kent͡ɕykuot͡ɕiaxaijaŋt͡ɕyt͡sueiɕinɕynʂɻ̩t͡ɕiant͡sʰet͡ɕiekuo，ʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂʰuanpuot͡ɕyliwokuoʈ͡ʂouʂant͡ɕinanjue350koŋli，t͡sanpukʰuaitueit͡ɕinanxaijuʂeŋtʰaixuant͡ɕiŋʈ͡ʂʰanʂeŋiŋɕiaŋ。

t͡ɕyt͡ɕieʂao，niŋɕijouweiniŋɕit͡ɕʰitʰianxuoʈ͡ʂejoutʰianpanʂeŋtʰianɻant͡ɕʰiniŋɕiʈ͡ʂʰulaitijeɕiaŋt͡sufen，jouʈ͡ʂʰeŋtʰianɻant͡ɕʰijou，t͡ɕʰiʈ͡ʂujaoʈ͡ʂʰeŋfenʂɻ̩C5~C11tʰiŋleitixunxeu。niŋɕijoutuot͡sʰunjukaojajout͡saŋʈ͡ʂoŋ，piŋt͡saitʰit͡ɕʰyxoujexua。niŋɕijoutilioufentuot͡sai20℃~200℃ʈ͡ʂɻ̩t͡ɕian，xueifaɕiŋxao，ʂɻ̩ʂeŋʈ͡ʂʰanɻoŋt͡ɕijoujouʈ͡ʂɻ̩tijuanliao。

t͡ɕypaotao，t͡sʰit͡sʰijoulunʈ͡ʂuaŋt͡sailiao13.6wantunniŋɕijou。kuot͡ɕiaxaijaŋxuant͡ɕiŋt͡ɕiant͡sʰeʈ͡ʂoŋɕinjant͡ɕioujuanjaot͡siweifenɕi，ʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂʰuanpuoʂaŋtiniŋɕijoujouxueifaɕiŋt͡ɕikao、iɻanipaoteŋtʰetian，ɻuʂueixoukʰuaikʰuaisuxueifa，ʂueimiant͡sʰanliouʂao，itanɕielout͡saikʰoŋt͡ɕʰiʈ͡ʂoŋmimanjumiŋxuoiint͡ɕʰixuot͡saipaoʈ͡ʂaʂɻ̩ku。t͡sʰiwai，pufenniŋɕijouliouxuat͡ɕʰiŋt͡ɕiliouʈ͡ʂʰunteŋxanliaŋt͡ɕiaokao，xueifat͡ɕiɻanʂaoxoukʰuaitueixaijaŋtait͡ɕʰit͡saoʈ͡ʂʰeŋitiŋtiuɻan。

joumeitʰiʈ͡ʂʰeŋ，t͡sʰit͡sʰitoŋxaixaijuʈ͡ʂuaŋʈ͡ʂʰuanʂɻ̩t͡si“weiwaŋ”xaoijouʂɻ̩kuilait͡sueitaitixaiʂaŋijouʂɻ̩ku。2002nian11jue，t͡saijou7.7wantunɻanliaojoutiɕilajoulun“weiwaŋ”xao，t͡saiɕipanjaɕipeiput͡ɕyxaian9koŋlitixaijujufeŋpaoʈ͡ʂʰenmuo，t͡ɕiɕipanjat͡saoʈ͡ʂʰeŋjanʈ͡ʂoŋtiuɻanxet͡ɕiŋt͡ɕisunʂɻ̩，jetueipʰutʰaojat͡saoʈ͡ʂʰeŋxentaitiiŋɕiaŋ。

kuot͡ɕiaxaijaŋt͡ɕypeixaixaijaŋxuant͡ɕiŋt͡ɕiant͡sʰeʈ͡ʂoŋɕinjant͡ɕioujuanʈ͡ʂout͡ɕʰiŋɻenwei，ju“weiwaŋxao”suoɕieloutiɻanliaojouputʰoŋ，niŋɕijout͡ɕyjouxent͡ɕʰiaŋxueifaɕiŋ，ɕielouxoukʰuaikʰuaisuxueifa，ʂueimiant͡sʰanliout͡ɕiʂao，ɻ̩t͡ɕʰiepent͡sʰiʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂoŋʈ͡ʂʰuanʈ͡ʂɻ̩ɻeŋt͡saiɻanʂao，tailiaŋniŋɕijoukʰuaipeiɻanʂaofenɕie。tanʂɻ̩，niŋɕijoutueixaijaŋʂeŋtʰaixuant͡ɕiŋtiiŋɕiaŋjepuɻoŋxuʂɻ̩。niŋɕijousuoxanjoututiliouxuat͡ɕʰiŋt͡ɕiliouʈ͡ʂʰunteŋʈ͡ʂʰeŋfenxueifaxoukʰuaitueitait͡ɕʰit͡saoʈ͡ʂʰeŋuɻan，t͡ɕʰiɻanʂaoʈ͡ʂʰanujejouitiŋtuɕiŋ。t͡sʰiwai，ʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂʰuanpuopenʂenɕietaitiɻanliaojouitanɕielou，jekʰuaitueixuant͡ɕiŋʈ͡ʂʰanʂeŋiŋɕiaŋ。

ʈ͡ʂout͡ɕʰiŋpiaoʂɻ̩，kent͡ɕykuot͡ɕiaxaijaŋt͡ɕyɕianʈ͡ʂʰaŋt͡sueiɕinɕynʂɻ̩t͡ɕiant͡sʰet͡ɕiekuo，xait͡ɕianfeit͡ɕixaŋkʰoŋjaokanfaɕianʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂʰuantʰijouʈ͡ʂaijouʂaoliaŋisiijou。mut͡ɕʰian，ʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂʰuanpuot͡ɕyliwokuoʈ͡ʂouʂant͡ɕinanjue350koŋli，“kent͡ɕymut͡ɕʰianxaiʂaŋʂueiwent͡ɕʰiɕiaŋtʰiaot͡ɕian，womenɻenweiʂɻ̩kut͡sanpukʰuaitueit͡ɕinanxaijuʂeŋtʰaixuant͡ɕiŋʈ͡ʂʰanʂeŋiŋɕiaŋ。t͡ɕianit͡ɕiɕyt͡ɕiat͡ɕʰiaŋkent͡soŋt͡ɕiant͡sʰe，pʰiŋkutueixaijaŋʂeŋtʰaixuant͡ɕiŋtiiŋɕiaŋ。”

t͡sʰit͡ɕʰianjet͡seŋfaʂeŋkuoxaiʂaŋniŋɕijouʂɻ̩ku。jaot͡siweit͡ɕieʂao，xaiʂaŋniŋɕijouʂɻ̩kuʈ͡ʂujaot͡ɕiʈ͡ʂoŋt͡saiʂɻ̩jou（tʰianɻant͡ɕʰi）pʰiŋtʰaiant͡ɕʰyanʂɻ̩kufaŋmian。1988nian，iŋkuopeixaieɻ̩fapʰiŋtʰainiŋɕijouɕielouɕiŋʈ͡ʂʰeŋtitʰianɻant͡ɕʰijuntʰuanjumiŋxuofaʂeŋpaoʈ͡ʂa，t͡saoʈ͡ʂʰeŋ165ɻensiwaŋ，iŋkuopeixaijoutʰiant͡ɕianʈ͡ʂʰan12pʰa。kaiʂɻ̩kutʰiaoʈ͡ʂaʈ͡ʂɻ̩t͡ɕiet͡sʰueiʂeŋliaoʂɻ̩t͡ɕiet͡ɕitiHSE（t͡ɕiankʰaŋ、ant͡ɕʰyan、xuant͡ɕiŋ）piaoʈ͡ʂuntʰiɕitit͡ɕianli。2012nian，weijupeixaixaijutifakuotaotaɻ̩koŋsiaiɻ̩t͡ɕinjout͡ɕʰipʰiŋtʰaifaʂeŋtʰianɻant͡ɕʰiɕielouʂɻ̩ku。iniŋtueiteitaŋ，238miŋjuankoŋant͡ɕʰyanʈ͡ʂʰeli。tanʂɻ̩kutaoʈ͡ʂɻ̩pʰiŋtʰaiʈ͡ʂouweiʂueijuʈ͡ʂʰuɕianniŋɕijoutai，liʂɻ̩t͡ɕin2kejuet͡sʰaiwanʈ͡ʂʰeŋloutianfeŋtu。

waŋʈ͡ʂantʰikoŋtiŋweitankewei、xouɻ̩、xousan、t͡suliou、tanʂuaŋ、taiɕiao、taifakʰuai3t͡ɕixua，jouɻenkoŋʂoutoŋfapuʈ͡ʂɻ̩waŋʈ͡ʂan，kʰeneŋmeit͡ɕʰit͡ɕixuaxaomatifapuʂɻ̩t͡ɕianjou1-10miaoʂɻ̩t͡ɕiant͡sʰi。"3t͡ɕʰit͡ɕixua"ʂɻ̩joŋjut͡ɕiat͡ɕiaŋ70pʰaʈ͡ʂɻ̩93pʰa，ɻuot͡ɕiat͡ɕiaŋtʰaitikʰeneŋufaiŋli，ɻuotʰaikaokʰeneŋʂɻ̩ɕiaoxeipʰiŋtʰaiinjoupʰiant͡ɕʰian。

paitianfeŋsueiʂɻ̩iʈ͡ʂoŋʈ͡ʂʰaŋɕianpʰifupiŋʈ͡ʂeŋ，tanʂɻ̩int͡ɕʰipiŋinfut͡sa，iʈ͡ʂentuan、nanʈ͡ʂɻ̩liao，peiʂɻ̩t͡ɕieweiʂeŋt͡suʈ͡ʂɻ̩lieweiʂɻ̩taipʰifuwanʈ͡ʂeŋʈ͡ʂɻ̩i。paitianfeŋʈ͡ʂɻ̩piŋinsutuojuanxua，t͡ɕʰiejoufainsuʈ͡ʂoŋleifantuo。tʰatifaʂeŋpufennianliŋ、ɕiŋpie、tijuxeʈ͡ʂoŋt͡sutit͡ɕʰyfen。ipʰanlaiʂuo，paitianfeŋtifapiŋʂuaiʈ͡ʂʰeŋtiliŋxua、t͡ɕʰieɻuɕiŋmiŋɕiantuojunanɕiŋ。tueijufuʂait͡ɕiaoʂentiʈ͡ʂoŋt͡sut͡ɕʰifapiŋʂuaikaojufuʂait͡ɕʰiantiʈ͡ʂoŋt͡su。paitianfeŋtifapiŋpiŋmuojoutʰeiɕiŋtit͡ɕyetiŋinsu，ɻ̩iʈ͡ʂuaninsujeʂɻ̩t͡saixoutʰianxuant͡ɕiŋinsukoŋtʰoŋt͡suojoŋɕiaʈ͡ʂʰanʂeŋti。ɻ̩paitianfeŋtiʈ͡ʂɻ̩liaoliaoʈ͡ʂʰeŋ，jeʂɻ̩jouketʰit͡sʰiiti。it͡ɕypaitianfeŋpiŋintiputʰoŋ、piŋʈ͡ʂʰeŋtiʈ͡ʂaŋtuan、piŋlitifent͡ɕʰilait͡ɕinɕiŋʈ͡ʂɻ̩liao，feikʰoutʰoumiaoʂut͡ɕioukʰeiʈ͡ʂɻ̩tiŋʈ͡ʂɻ̩liaofaŋanti。

ninxao，xenkaoɕiŋneŋweininɕieta： mut͡ɕʰianʈ͡ʂɻ̩liaopaitianfeŋtiliaofajouxentuo，putʰoŋtipiŋt͡ɕʰiŋ，ketʰit͡sʰiiputʰoŋ，ʈ͡ʂɻ̩liaofaŋfajeʂɻ̩puijaŋ，t͡ɕianixuanʈ͡ʂejaot͡ɕianʈ͡ʂat͡ɕʰiŋʈ͡ʂʰu，t͡saitueiʈ͡ʂeŋʈ͡ʂɻ̩liao，t͡sʰaineŋtataojut͡ɕʰitiʈ͡ʂɻ̩liaoɕiaokuo。maŋmuʈ͡ʂɻ̩liao，put͡ɕinlaŋfeit͡ɕʰianmuoɕiaokuopuʂuo，joutifanɻ̩kʰuait͡ɕiaʈ͡ʂoŋpiŋt͡ɕʰiŋ。GX-pixeiʂaisuɕipaopʰeiʈ͡ʂɻ̩ʈ͡ʂu...

